        {
            "+content": "The inhabitents of the continent of Cruzon have the ability to manipulate quartz, which they use to power their machines and vehicles. They call this \"magic\", and only Rygart Arrow lacks this ability. As a teenager, he went to school with Hodr, who became the king of his country, and Zess, who was the brother of the military commander of Athens. When his country, Krishna, goes into war against the neighbouring kingdom of Athens, he might be the only one able to stop the war between two friends, because he is the only person able to pilot an ancient golem that cannot be used by magic users.",
